@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json

### Test 1: Check if API is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Test 2: Generate checklist from text (Simple assignment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/assignment-checklist
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "assignmentContent": "Write a 5-page essay on climate change. Include introduction, 3 body paragraphs with evidence, and conclusion. Due December 15. Use at least 5 academic sources."
}

### Test 3: Generate checklist from complex assignment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/assignment-checklist
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "assignmentContent": "Complete a research project on renewable energy sources. Requirements: 1) Introduction explaining the importance of renewable energy 2) Detailed analysis of solar energy (types, efficiency, advantages/disadvantages) 3) Detailed analysis of wind energy (technology, scalability, environmental impact) 4) Comparison section analyzing pros and cons of both 5) Conclusion with recommendations. Submit as PDF with at least 8 academic sources. Due: December 20, 2026. This should be 10-15 pages long."
}

### Test 4: Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### Test 5: Get all courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses
